%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Highway%20Construction%20Slows%2C%20Has%20Met%20Only%2045%25%20of%20its%20Target%20in%20Current%20Fiscal%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11105131%2Fyamuna-expressway-385360_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Highway%20construction%20slowed%20down%20during%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%2C%20and%20has%20met%20only%2045%25%20of%20its%20target%20of%2013%2C800%20km%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Froad-work-slows-down-only-45-of-target-met-11707481012245.html%5C%22%3Enews%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Cem%3ELiveMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20is%20despite%20the%20Union%20government%20earmarking%20a%20record%20Rs%202.16%20trillion%20capex%20in%20the%20first%20nine%20months%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20quoted%20data%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20(MoRTH)%2C%20which%20said%20that%20India%20has%20added%206%2C216%20km%20of%20national%20highways%20in%20April-December%202023.%20This%20is%20only%2045%25%20of%20the%2013%2C800%20km%20construction%20target%20for%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20falling%20short%20is%20not%20new.%20Though%20it%20faced%20a%20target%20of%2012%2C500%20km%2C%20the%20government%20built%20only%2010%2C457%20km%20of%20roads%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%20of%202022%2C%20and%2010%2C331%20km%20in%202023.%20This%20year%20%E2%80%93%20FY2024%20%E2%80%93%20the%20target%20is%2013%2C800%20km.%20The%20news%20report%20quoted%20an%20anonymous%20source%20in%20the%20know%20who%20said%20that%20achieving%20this%20target%20is%20unlikely%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20India%20has%20added%206%2C216%20km%20of%20national%20highways%20this%20year%20which%20is%20still%20higher%20than%20in%202023%20(when%20only%20about%205%2C744%20km%20of%20work%20was%20completed%20till%20the%20end%20of%20December).%20Sources%20also%20quoted%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20delay%20in%20awarding%20road%20projects%20as%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20highway%20construction%20slowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20slowing%20down%20has%20come%20despite%20the%20government%20increasing%20its%20capital%20expenditure%20to%20Rs%202%2C15%2C910%20crore%2C%20or%2083.49%25%20of%20the%20record%20high%20capex%20outlay%20of%20Rs%202%2C58%2C606%20crore%20for%20FY2024%2C%20the%20news%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20rating%20agency%20ICRA%20suggests%20that%20highway%20awards%20slow%20down%20in%20the%20last%20quarter%20of%20a%20financial%20year%20that%20comes%20just%20before%20elections.%20If%20this%20happens%20this%20year%20with%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20construct%20over%2080%20km%20of%20highways%20every%20day%20in%20the%20last%20three%20months%2C%20the%20news%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707630342000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11105131%2Fyamuna-expressway-385360_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhighway-construction-slows-has-met-only-45-of-its-target-in-current-fiscal-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20added%20only%206%2C216%20km%20of%20national%20highways%20during%20April-December%202023%2C%20against%20a%20target%20of%2013%2C800%20km%20for%20this%20fiscal%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhighway-construction-slows-has-met-only-45-of-its-target-in-current-fiscal-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Compromise%20Over%20Ram%26quot%3B%3A%20Acharya%20Krishnam%20After%20Congress%20Expels%20Him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAcharya%20Pramod%20Krishnam%2C%20a%20spiritual%20leader%2C%20hit%20back%20at%20Congress%20a%20day%20after%20