%20been%20participating%20in%20the%20Big%20Ticket%20draws%20for%20the%20past%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20This%20time%20around%2C%20the%20first-time%20lottery%20winner%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20decided%20to%20select%20the%20tickets%20with%20numbers%207%20and%2013%2C%20which%20are%20the%20birth%20dates%20of%20their%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20victory%2C%20in%20conversation%20with%20the%20Khaleej%20Times%2C%20Mr%20Arikkatt%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20residing%20in%20Al%20Ain%20for%20more%20than%2010%20years.%20I%20have%20been%20purchasing%20tickets%20for%20the%20past%203%20years.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20I%20have%20won%20a%20lottery.%20This%20time%2C%20me%20and%20my%20wife%20selected%20tickets%20with%20numbers%207%20and%2013%2C%20which%20are%20the%20birth%20dates%20of%20our%20children.%20Two%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20missed%20Dh1%20million%20by%20a%20whisker%20with%20the%20same%20combination%2C%20but%20this%20time%20I%20was%20fortunate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20his%20feelings%20after%20the%20big%20announcement%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20speechless.%20I%20couldn't%20describe%20the%20feelings%20in%20words.%20I%20recognised%20Richard's%20voice%2C%20as%20I%20had%20been%20listening%20to%20it%20for%20years.%20I%20knew%20he%20called%20the%20winners%2C%20but%20I%20never%20imagined%20it%20was%20the%20first%20prize.%20It%20was%20a%20surprise.%20This%20is%20a%20life-changing%20moment%2C%20not%20just%20for%20me%20but%20for%20others%20in%20our%20group.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707629100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F7oor2io8_rajeev-arikkatt_625x300_10_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fmeet-rajeev-arikkatt-the-indian-expat-who-won-rs-33-crore-uae-jackpot-5035608%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bdream%20come%2