hir's%20ideology%20was%20defined%20by%20his%20experiences%20in%20a%20world%20driven%20by%20brutal%20market%20forces.%20Son%20of%20a%20wealthy%20father%2C%20he%20was%20brought%20up%20by%20his%20mother%20in%20poverty%20after%20he%20chose%20the%20latter%20during%20a%20court%20hearing.%20Sahir%20saw%20and%20felt%20inequality%20up%2C%20close%20and%20personal.%20And%20tangibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Danish%20Husain%20in%20Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Danish%20Husain%20in%20Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fqm3sg2fg_danish_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanish%20Husain%20in%20'Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun'%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Nishtha%20Gautam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20pre-independence%20India%2C%20Sahir%20worked%20in%20Lahore%20as%20an%20editor%20only%20to%20be%20underpaid%2C%20and%2C%20consequently%2C%20underpaying%20his%20writer-contributors.%20He%20was%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20unfairness%20of%20the%20situation.%20As%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Progressive%20Writers'%20Association%20and%20a%20proponent%20of%20Communism%2C%20Sahir%20earned%20a%20reputation%20that%20went%20beyond%20his%20literary%20genius.%20But%20the%20late%201940s%20were%20dangerous%20years%20for%20any%20%3Cem%3Esurkha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20literally%20meaning%20'Red-coloured'%2C%20intellectual.%20The%20government%20of%20Pakistan%20was%20too%20eager%20to%20put%20this%20young%20poet%20behind%20bars.%20Sahir%20fled%20to%20Delhi%20and%20carried%20some%20trauma%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanish%2C%20playing%20Sahir%20in%20the%20play%2C%20brings%20out%20all%20the%20poet's%20struggles%20through%20his%20powerful%2C%20personalised%20storytelling.%20Never%20leaving%20the%20character%2C%20he%20often%20breaks%20the%20fourth%20wall%20to%20address%20the%20audience.%20That%20his%20words-Sahir's%20words-seemingly%20address%20the%20audience%20of%20today%20is%20a%20function%20of%20Sahir's%20eternal%20relevance.%20As%20long%20as%20there%20is%20inequality%20in%20the%20world%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20Sahir%20verse%20addressing%2C%20highlighting%20it.%20On%20top%20of%20it%2C%20Danish's%20own%20poetic%20sensibility%2C%20complete%20with%20his%20politics%2C%20adds%20a%20distinct%20flavour%20to%20Sahir's%20words%20even%20almost%2045%20years%20after%20the%20latter's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahir%20has%20often%20been%20straitjacketed%20as%20the%20poet%20of%20despondency%20and%20melancholia%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20eternal%20lyrics%20for%20films%20like%20Pyasa.%20A%20contemporary%20of%20Faiz%20Ahmed%20Faiz%2C%20he%2C%20too%2C%20has%20an%20answer%20to%20this%20charge.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EHam%20ghamzada%20hain%3Cbr%3E%5CnLaayen%20kahan%20se%20khushi%20ke%20geet%2C%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnDenge%20wohijo%20paayenge%20is%20zindagi%20se%20ham%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Faiz%2C%20his%20poetry%2C%20too%2C%20is%20not%20created%20in%20a%20vacuum%3B%20cultural%20materialism%20informs%20both%20the%20poets.%20And%20it%20informs%20the%20art%20of%20poet-performer%20Danish%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Danish%20Husain%20in%20Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Danish%20Husain%20in%20Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fo2k20p5_danish_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanish%20Husain%20in%20'Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun'%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Nishtha%20Gautam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20of%20events%20and%20verses%20to%20weave%20together%20Sahir's%20biography%20is%20a%20clear%20testimony%20of%20Danish's%20indictment%20of%20communalism%2C%20hierarchy-driven%20literary%20world%2C%20gender%20inequality%2C%20populism%2C%20class%20inequities%2C%20hypocritical%20politics%20of%20the%20day%2C%20and%20the%20marginal%20status%20of%20artistic%20genius%20in%20the%20commercial%20enterprise%20of%20filmmaking.%20Danish%2C%20it%20appears%2C%20uses%20Sahir's%20words%20to%20express%20his%20own%20dissatisfactions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EOn%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Sahir%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%3Cem%3E%20Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20dramatic%20thrust%20is%20on%20the%20ebbs%20and%20tides%20of%20Sahir's%20personal%20and%20professional%20life-both%20going%20back%20to%20his%20mother%20through%20an%20invisible%20umbilical%20cord%20that%20he%20could%20never%20detach.%20Sahir's%20deep%20attachment%20with%20and%20respect%20for%20his%20mother%20became%20a%20leitmotif%20for%20all%20his%20relationships%20with%20women.%20A%20vocal%20advocate%20of%20women's%20rights%2C%20Sahir's%20feminism%20perhaps%20came%20with%20a%20hefty%20price%20tag.%20None%20of%20his%20romantic%20relationships%20survived%20his%20radical%20attitudes.%20He%20was%20not%20the%20man%20to%20challenge%20the%20choices%20his%20women%20made%2C%20especially%20when%20his%20emotional%20limitations%20disallowed%20any%20blossoming%20of%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20Sahir's%20love%20poetry%20is%20as%20powerful%20as%20his%20'social-cause'%20verses.%20The%20play%20makes%20use%20of%20some%20of%20his%20best-known%20verses%20written%20for%20Hindi%20cinema%2C%20including%20%3Cem%3EJaane%20Kya%20Tune%20Kahi%2C%20Kabhi%20Kabhi%20Mere%20Dil%20Mein%2C%20and%20Abhi%20Na%20Jaao%20Chhodkar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20important%20thing%20about%20Sahir's%20love%20poetry%20is%20the%20beloved's%20positioning%20as%20an%20equal%20partner.%20She's%20neither%20a%20coy%20mistress%20nor%20the%20lady-on-a-high-pedestal%20of%20the%20courtly%20love%20tradition.%20Unrequited%20and%20unconsummated%2C%20Sahir's%20love%20moves%20and%20revels%20in%20unchartered%20territory.%20This%20reviewer%20feels%20that%20the%20inclusion%20of%20'%3Cem%3EChalo%20Ek%20Baar%20Phir%20Se%20Ajnabi%20Ban%20Jaye%20Hum%20Dono%3C%2Fem%3E'%20in%20the%20play%20would%20have%20reinforced%20this%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20theatre%20festival%20of%20the%20National%20School%20of%20Drama%20this%20year%20opens%20with%20%3Cem%3EMain%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun%3C%2Fem%3E.%20After%20houseful%20shows%20at%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20the%20Performing%20Arts%20(NCPA)%20and%20the%20Prithvi%20Theatre%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20this%20will%20be%20Danish's%20first%20outing%20in%20Delhi%20as%20Sahir.%20Javed%20Akhtar%20was%20a%20much%20younger%20colleague%20of%20Sahir%20in%20the%20worlds%20of%20cinema%20and%20Urdu%20poetry.%20They%20were%20also%20close%20friends.%20Sahir's%20influence%20is%20writ%20large%20in%20Javed%20Akhtar's%20poetry%20of%20resistance%20and%20rebelliousness.%20Danish%2C%20a%20much%20younger%20poet%2C%20has%20not%20had%20the%20same%20fortune.%20But%20he%20has%20found%20a%20way%20to%20claim%20Sahir's%20legacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanish%20becomes%20Sahir.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707628020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fiuobvf3g_danish_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhen-urdu-poet-sahir-surkha-ludhianvi-met-danish-daastaango-5035430%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20'Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun'%2C%20which%20opens%20this%20year's%20theatre%20festival%20of%20the%20National%20School%20of%20Drama%2C%20actor-playwright-director%20Danish%20Husain%20gives%20Sahir%20Ludhianvi-the%20man%20an%20edge%20over%2