%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107595710.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMithun%20Chakraborty%20was%20admitted%20to%20Apollo%20Multispeciality%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20after%20suffering%20an%20Ischemic%20Cerebrovascular%20Stroke.%20Minor%20symptoms%20include%20speech%20difficulty%20and%20affected%20right%20hand%20movement.%20Family%20confirms%20routine%20check-up%3B%20Mahaakshay%20and%20Madalsa%20confirm%20stable%20condition.%20Manager%20Vijay%20dismisses%20panic%2C%20states%20Mithun%20is%20fine%20and%20shooting%20in%20Kolkata.%20Hospital%20confirms%20conscious%20and%20well-oriented.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Politics%20Bounces%20Back%20in%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25140239%2FPakistan-elections.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20dust%20settles%20on%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20recently%20concluded%20elections%2C%20some%20underlying%20facts%20will%20come%20into%20clearer%20focus%2C%20namely%20the%20further%20entrenchment%20of%20devolved%20and%20accommodative%20democratic%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20first%20the%20dust.%20The%20resilience%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaaf%20(PTI)%20is%2C%20obviously%20enough%2C%20the%20big%20story.%20After%20he%20had%20fallen%20out%20with%20his%20former%20mentors%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20%E2%80%98establishment%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20euphemism%20for%20the%20armed%20forces%E2%80%99%20extra-constitutional%20political%20power%20%E2%80%93%20he%20ended%20up%20in%20detention%2C%20and%20his%20party%20was%20put%20under%20legal%20and%20extra-legal%20pressures.%20In%20what%20became%20a%20test%20of%20their%20organisational%20ability%2C%20the%20party%20was%20unable%20to%20retain%20a%20unified%20election%20symbol%20and%20its%20nominees%20were%20forced%20to%20contest%20the%20elections%20as%20independent%20candidates.%20Despite%20these%20disadvantages%20and%20of%20course%2C%20the%20absence%20from%20the%20campaign%20of%20its%20popular%20leader%2C%20PTI%20managed%20to%20win%20more%20seats%20than%20any%20other%20party%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20and%20got%20a%20landslide%20majority%20in%20the%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province.%20It%20also%20went%20neck%20and%20neck%20with%20Nawaz%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(N)%20in%20the%20most%20populous%20Punjab%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20supporters%20who%20are%20prone%20to%20grandiose%20historical%20comparisons%20are%20incorrect%20in%20claiming%20that%20either%20their%20persecution%20or%20their%20performance%20was%20unprecedented.%20Claims%20of%20bias%20are%20valid%20but%20do%20not%20amount%20to%20egregious%20deviations%20from%20past%20practice.%20The%20violence%20unleashed%20by%20the%20Musharraf%20regime%20and%20its%20alleged%20collaborators%20before%20the%202008%20elections%20against%20its%20opponents%20claimed%20hundreds%20of%20lives%20including%20that%20of%20Benazir%20Bhutto.%20In%20the%202013%20elections%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP)%20selectively%20threatened%20and%20then%20attacked%20campaigns%20of%20three%20parties%20(PPP%2C%20ANP%20and%20MQM)%2C%20murdering%20party%20supporters%20and%20kidnapping%20the%20son%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Yusuf%20Raza%20Gillani%20from%20a%20campaign%20event.%20The%20persecution%20of%20PMLN%20leaders%20and%20candidates%20in%202018%20was%2C%20arguably%2C%20no%20less%20severe%20than%20what%20PTI%20faced%20this%20time%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20defiance%20and%20%E2%80%98bounce%E2%80%99%20are%20also%20not%20unprecedented.%20The%20PPP%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20its%20charismatic%20leader%20went%20on%20to%20fight%20and%20win%20the%202008%20elections%20on%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%9Cdemocracy%20is%20the%20best%20revenge%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20the%20PMLN%20made%20a%20good%20showing%20in%202018%20on%20the%20chant%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Evote%20ko%20izzat%20do%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Crespect%20the%20vote%E2%80%9D.%20PTI%20joined%20the%20ranks%20of%20other%20parties%20when%20it%20too%20turned%20to%20the%20ballot%20as%20its%20primary%20form%20of%20protest%20calling%20for%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ezulm%20ka%20badla%3C%2Fem%3E%20vote%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cvote%20to%20avenge%20injustice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20comes%20next%20is%20complicated%20for%20both%20the%20PTI%20and%20the%20establishment.%20Khan%20would%20want%20to%20use%20the%20electoral%20resilience%20of%20his%20party%20to%20negotiate%20with%20the%20establishment%20for%20his%20way%20out%20of%20detention%20and%20court%20cases%2C%20and%20possibly%20back%20into%20office.%20But%20while%20the%20political%20wind%20might%20be%20with%20him%2C%20parliamentary%20arithmetic%20is%20not.%20According%20to%20results%20already%20published%20by%20the%20election%20commission%2C%20PTI%20supported%20independents%20would%20constitute%20the%20largest%20bloc%20in%20the%20national%20assembly%20but%20fall%20well%20short%20of%20an%20overall%20majority.%20PTI%20leaders%20claim%20that%20they%20have%20been%20cheated%20out%20of%20many%20seats%20and%20that%20if%20awarded%20they%20would%20have%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20national%20and%20Punjab%20assemblies.%20Some%2C%20though%20not%20all%2C%20such%20claims%20might%20be%20valid%2C%20but%20legal%20challenges%20to%20declared%20results%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20long%20drawn%20affairs%20with%20no%20guarantee%20of%20success.%20In%20the%20meanwhile%20parliamentary%20business%20will%20need%20to%20be%20attended%20to%2C%20and%20PMLN%20with%20somewhat%20fewer%20seats%20than%20PTI%2C%20but%20with%20ongoing%20relationships%20with%20other%20parties%20and%20non-PTI%20independents%2C%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20might%20be%20tempted%20to%20use%20the%20momentum%20of%20its%20election%20win%20to%20switch%20to%20protest%20mode%E2%80%93%20about%20election%20irregularities%20and%20then%20about%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20detention.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20fondness%20and%20ability%20to%20elevate%20his%20own%20person%20to%20a%20point%20of%20principle%20means%20that%20he%20might%20well%20demand%20this%20of%20his%20followers.%C2%A0%20One%20example%20of%20such%20audacity%20was%20the%20failed%20attempt%20at%20%E2%80%98insurrection%E2%80%99%20on%20May%209%2C%202023%20when%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20staged%20violent%20attacks%20on%20state%20symbols%20and%20military%20facilities%20in%20protest%20against%20his%20detention%20in%20a%20court%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20Have%20the%20Pakistan%20Elections%20Made%20the%20Country%E2%80%99s%20Crisis%20Worse%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-have-the-pakistan-elections-made-the-countrys-crisis-worse%5C%22%3EHave%20the%20Pakistan%20Elections%20Made%20the%20Country%E2%80%99s%20Crisis%20Worse%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlternatively%2C%20PTI%20winning%20candidates%20might%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20humdrum%20processes%20of%20parliamentary%20politics%2C%20while%20keeping%20up%20lip%20service%20about%20the%20plight%20of%20their%20detained%20leader.%20They%20have%20an%20incontrovertible%20claim%20to%20forming%20the%20provincial%20government%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20and%20would%20constitute%20a%20powerful%20opposition%20in%20Punjab%20and%20in%20Islamabad.%20Getting%20involved%20in%20parliamentary%20politics%20and%20in%20returning%20to%20office%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20would%20involve%20some%20level%20of%20autonomy%20from%20the%20whims%20of%20their%20popular%20leader.%20And%20it%20may%20expose%20them%20to%20fissures%20and%20factionalism.%20This%20process%20will%20start%20as%20soon%20as%20a%20few%20days%20from%20now%20when%20the%20PTI%20group%20will%20have%20to%20agree%20on%20parliamentary%20tactics%20and%20leadership%20positions%20nationally%20and%20in%20Punjab%2C%20and%20government%20formation%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conundrum%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98establishment%E2%80%99%20is%20no%20less%20complicated.%20The%20PTI%20was%20mentored%20into%20office%20in%202018%20to%20disrupt%20political%20accommodation%20between%20the%20PMLN%20and%20the%20PPP%20which%20was%20seen%20as%20encroaching%20upon%20the%20extra-constitutional%20powers%20of%20the%20establishment.%20Successive%20constitutional%20and%20legislative%20changes%20particularly%20the%2018th%20Constitutional%20Amendment%2C%20the%20completion%20of%20parliamentary%20terms%2C%20and%20rival%20parties%20leading%20the%20various%20provincial%20and%20federal%20governments%20were%20all%20indicators%20of%20the%20consolidation%20of%20the%20political%20system.%20The%20PTI%20echoed%20the%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20distaste%20for%20political%20accommodation%2C%20and%20its%20charismatic%20leader%20magnified%20the%20narrative%20that%20politics%20and%20professional%20politicians%20are%20all%20about%20self-serving%20deal-making.%20He%20threatened%20to%20disrupt%20this%20system%20and%20to%20replace%20it%20with%20a%20more%20unitarian%20model%20with%20himself%20at%20the%20helm%20ably%20assisted%20by%20the%20establishment.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20political%20ambitions%20brought%20him%20into%20conflict%20with%20his%20erstwhile%20mentors%20whose%20designated%20role%20for%20him%20was%20to%20disrupt%20the%20PMLN-PPP%20compact%20but%20who%20had%20not%20thought%20things%20through%20beyond%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20establishment%20needs%20to%20hold%20Khan%20down%20because%20he%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20an%20unreliable%20interlocutor.%20It%20has%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20accept%20broader%20accommodation%20between%20the%20other%20political%20parties.%20Perhaps%20the%20most%20remarkable%20but%20unnoticed%20feature%20of%20the%20election%20results%20is%20the%20continuity%20in%20the%20popular%20mandate.%20The%20number%20of%20seats%20won%20by%20the%20main%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20notably%20PTI%2C%20PMLN%2C%20PPP%20%E2%80%93%20is%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20outcome%20in%202018.%20And%20as%20in%202018%2C%20the%20PTI%20has%20won%20a%20majority%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20the%20PPP%20in%20Sindh%2C%20while%20Punjab%20remains%20split%20down%20the%20middle.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%202024%20elections%20represent%20the%20third%20successive%20PTI%20win%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20and%20the%20fourth%20one%20for%20the%20PPP%20in%20Sindh.%20Party%20positions%20in%20national%20assembly%20seats%20from%20the%20provinces%20correspond%20closely%20with%20provincial%20assembly%20outcomes.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98national%E2%80%99%20leader%20has%20not%20dented%20the%20silent%20but%20steady%20shift%20of%20the%20centre%20of%20political%20gravity%20from%20Islamabad%20to%20the%20provincial%20capitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElection%20results%20demonstrated%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20and%20the%20resilience%20of%20his%20party.%20But%20they%20do%20not%20change%20other%20salient%20facts.%20The%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20at%20cornering%20politicians%20through%20the%20anti-politics%20Khan%20was%20hoisted%20on%20its%20own%20petard.%20The%20failure%20of%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20attempted%20%E2%80%98insurrection%E2%80%99%20of%20May%202023%20still%20looms%20heavy%20and%20there%20will%20be%20little%20appetite%20among%20his%20supporters%20or%20the%20public%20at%20large%20for%20the%20renewal%20of%20street%20protests%20in%20Punjab.%20In%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20the%20PTI%20will%20have%20little%20reason%20to%20protest%2C%20as%20it%20is%20called%20upon%20to%20form%20a%20government%2C%20sending%20its%20legislators%20and%20their%20supporters%20scrambling%20for%20office%20and%20favour.%20The%20establishment%20and%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20the%20two%20implacable%20opponents%20of%20devolved%20and%20accommodative%20democratic%20politics%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20have%20played%20each%20other%20to%20a%20stalemate.%20Elected%20politicians%2C%20in%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20their%20work%20cut%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHaris%20Gazdar%20is%20Senior%20Researcher%2C%20Collective%20for%20Social%20Science%20Research%2C%20Karachi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707627867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25140239%2FPakistan-elections.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpolitics-bounces-back-in-pakistan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20establishment%20and%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20the%20two%20implacable%20opponents%20of%20devolved%20and%20accommodative%20democratic%20politics%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20have%20played%20each%20other%20to%20a%20stalemate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpolitics-bounces-back-in-pakistan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taylor%20Swift%20reaches%20LA%20ahead%20of%20Super%20Bowl%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707627790000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107595914%2Cimgsize-43040.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Ftaylor-swift-touches-down-los-angeles-ahead-of-travis-kelces-super-bowl-game%2Farticleshow%2F107595687.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107595687.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPop%20megastar%20Taylor%20Swift%20will%20attend%20the%20Super%20Bowl%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20to%20support%20her%20boyfriend%2C%20Chiefs'%20Travis%20Kelce.%20After%20the%20game%2C%20she%20will%20fly%20to%20Australia%20for%20her%20sold-out%20concerts.%20Swift%20recently%20won%20her%20fourth%20Grammy%20and%20is%20a%20loyal%20Chiefs%20fan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%20Turns%20Off%20Phone%20Internet%2C%20Blocks%20Borders%20To%20Stop%20Farmers'%20March%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMobile%20internet%20connectivity%20has%20been%20suspended%20in%20seven%20districts%20as%20the%20BJP-led%20Haryana%20government%20gears%20up%20to%20block%20the%20farmers'%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20government%20has%20issued%20a%20notification%2C%20saying%20dongle%20services%20provided%20on%20mobile%20phones%2C%20will%20remain%20suspended%20and%20only%20voice%20calls%20would%20go%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20are%20demanding%20a%20law%20to%20guarantee%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20for%20their%20produce%20and%20pension%20and%20insurance%20schemes.%20More%20than%20200%20organisations%20are%20part%20of%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMobile%20internet%20services%20have%20been%20suspended%20in%20Ambala%2C%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Kaithal%2C%20Jind%2C%20Hisar%2C%20Fatehabad%20and%20Sirsa%20districts%20till%20Tuesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20planned%20to%20seal%20Haryana-Punjab%20borders%20to%20ensure%20protesting%20farmers%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20state%20cannot%20enter%20Haryana%20before%20proceeding%20to%20Delhi.%20This%20move%20will%20inconvenience%20those%20travelling%20between%20Chandigarh%20and%20Delhi.%20Police%20have%20announced%20alternative%20routes%20for%20this%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20Police%20have%20advised%20commuters%20to%20avoid%20arterial%20roads%20on%20Tuesday.%20It%20has%20also%20warned%20of%20traffic%20disruption%20due%20to%20the%20protest.%20On%20the%20borders%20between%20Haryana%20and%20Delhi%2C%20cement%20barriers%2C%20barbed%20wires%20and%20sandbags%20are%20in%20place%20to%20stop%20the%20farmers%20from%20crossing%20into%20the%20national%20capital.%20Water%20cannons%20and%20drones%20have%20also%20been%20brought%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifty%20companies%20of%20paramilitary%20forces%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20assist%20Haryana%20Police.%20Haryana%20police%20chief%20Shatrujeet%20Kapur%20warned%20of%20taking%20strict%20action%20if%20anyone%20tries%20to%20disrupt%20peace.%20The%20police%20have%20asked%20farmers%20to%20stay%20away%20and%20also%20warned%20of%20action%20if%20public%20property%20is%20damaged.%20Haryana%20Home%20Minister%20Anil%20Vij%2C%20too%2C%20has%20said%20the%20state%20government%20%26quot%3Bwill%20ensure%20complete%20peace%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20invited%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20for%20talks%20tomorrow.%20But%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20the%20meeting%20will%20result%20in%20the%20farmers%20calling%20off%20protests%20because%20the%20demands%20require%20detailed%20discussion%20and%20parliamentary%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20is%20being%20organised%20by%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-political)%20and%20several%20farmers'%20organisations%20have%20distanced%20itself%20from%20it.%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Lakhowal)%2C%20which%20was%20part%20of%20the%20farmers'%20protest%20in%202020-21%20that%20led%20to%20the%20Centre%20withdrawing%20three%20laws%2C%20said%20they%20won't%20join%20Tuesday's%20protest.%20Instead%2C%20they%20will%20participate%20in%20a%20protest%20on%20Friday.%20The%20BKU%2C%20however%2C%20warned%20that%20if%20farmers%20part%20of%20Tuesday's%20protest%20are%20%26quot%3Bmanhandled%26quot%3B%2C%20all%20unions%20will%20hit%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707627720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2gka4fi8_haryana-border_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-mobile-internet-off-barriers-ready-haryana-preps-to-stop-farmers-march-5035469%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mobile%20internet%20connectivity%20has%20been%20suspended%20in%20seven%20districts%20as%20the%20BJP-led%20Haryana%20government%20gears%20up%20to%20block%20the%20farmers'%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-mobile-internet-off-barriers-ready-haryana-preps-to-stop-farmers-march-5035469%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-mobile-internet-off-barriers-ready-haryana-preps-to-stop-farmers-march-5035469%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-mobile-internet-off-barriers-ready-haryana-preps-to-stop-farmers-march-5035469%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20To%20Soon%20Launch%20GPS-Based%20Toll%20Collection%3A%20Here's%20How%20It%20Will%20Work%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThose%20pesky%20toll%20plazas%20that%20interrupt%20smooth%20drives%20may%20be%20on%20their%20way%20out.%20Union%20minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20announced%20that%20GPS-based%20toll%20collection%20systems%20will%20replace%20existing%20highway%20toll%20plazas%20in%20the%20country.%20Road%2C%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20minister%20announced%20that%20transition%20will%20occur%20as%20early%20as%20April%20this%20year.%20The%20government%20has%20appointed%20a%20consultant%20to%20implement%20a%20GPS-based%20toll%20collection%20system%20on%20national%20highways%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20Minister%20also%20said%20the%20system%20will%20be%20introduced%20on%20a%20pilot%20basis%20in%20addition%20to%20FASTags.%20The%20move%20is%20aimed%20at%20reducing%20traffic%20congestion%20and%20charging%20motorists%20for%20the%20exact%20distance%20travelled%20on%20the%20highways.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gadkari%20had%20earlier%20said%20state-owned%20NHAI's%20toll%20revenue%20is%20currently%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%20and%20it%20is%20going%20to%20soar%20to%20Rs%201.40%20lakh%20crore%20in%202-3%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20is%20looking%20at%20new%20technologies%20including%20GPS-based%20toll%20systems%20to%20replace%20toll%20plazas%20in%20the%20country...We%20will%20bring%20new%20technology%20in%20six%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%202018-19%2C%20the%20average%20waiting%20time%20for%20vehicles%20at%20toll%20plaza%20was%208%20minutes.%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20FASTags%20during%202020-21%20and%202021-22%2C%20the%20average%20waiting%20time%20of%20the%20vehicles%20was%20reduced%20to%2047%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202021%2C%20FASTags%20became%20mandatory%20for%20all%20vehicles%20to%20pay%20tolls%20on%20highways.%20Vehicles%20without%20FASTags%20are%20required%20to%20pay%20double%20the%20toll%20fee%20as%20a%20fine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%20is%20considerable%20improvement%20in%20waiting%20time%20at%20certain%20locations%2C%20especially%20near%20cities%2C%20in%20densely-populated%20towns%2C%20there%20are%20still%20some%20delays%20at%20toll%20plazas%20during%20peak%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20GPS-Based%20Toll%20System%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GPS-based%20electronic%20toll%20collection%20system%20will%20use%20an%20automatic%20number%20plate%20recognition%20(ANPR)%20system%20through%20cameras%20installed%20on%20highways%20and%20deduct%20tolls%20based%20on%20the%20distance%20travelled%20by%20a%20vehicle.%20At%20present%2C%20FASTags%20uses%20RFID-based%20toll%20collection%20at%20plazas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20device%20monitors%20your%20movements%20while%20driving%2C%20accurately%20marking%20your%20entry%20and%20exit%20points%20on%20tolled%20segments.%20By%20analyzing%20your%20travel%20distance%2C%20it%20identifies%20the%20toll%20plazas%20you've%20passed%20through%20and%20computes%20the%20charges%20accordingly.%20This%20eliminates%20the%20uniformity%20of%20fixed%20tolls%20at%20booths%2C%20ensuring%20fairness%20for%20drivers%20traversing%20shorter%20distances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20drivers%20on%20the%20road%20are%20relieved%20from%20concerns%20about%20handling%20cash%2C%20waiting%20for%20change%2C%20or%20checking%20their%20FASTag%20account%20balance.%20The%20toll%20fee%20is%20automatically%20deducted%20from%20your%20linked%20account%20using%20a%20secure%20electronic%20payment%20system.%20This%20process%20also%20eradicates%20human%20errors%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20toll%20evasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707627600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F0452k2pg_mumbai-airport-fastag-lane-large_625x300_15_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-soon-launch-gps-based-toll-collection-heres-how-it-will-work-5035582%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20GPs-based%20electronic%20toll%20collection%20system%20will%20use%20an%20automatic%20number%20plate%20recognition%20(ANPR)%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-soon-launch-gps-based-toll-collection-heres-how-it-will-work-5035582%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-soon-launch-gps-based-toll-collection-heres-how-it-will-work-5035582%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-soon-launch-gps-based-toll-collection-heres-how-it-will-work-5035582%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Box%20Office%3A%20Deepika%20Padukone's%20Fighter%20Is%20A%20Few%20Crores%20From%20200%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com