ance%20that%20that%20trial%20is%20going%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-wants-trumps-classified-documents-trial-done-by-september-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehappen%20before%20the%20November%20election%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20of%20course%2C%20if%20Trump%20is%20elected%20and%20he%20regains%20control%20of%20the%20White%20House%2C%20the%20prosecution%20goes%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECannon%20has%20already%20been%20reversed%20once%20on%20appeal%20by%20the%2011th%20Circuit%20in%20this%20case%2C%20when%20she%20moved%20to%20appoint%20a%20special%20master%20to%20oversee%20the%20review%20of%20classified%20documents%20seized%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-attempted-delete-mar-a-lago-footage-doj-indictment-classified-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMar-A-Lago%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%2011th%20Circuit%20court%20sided%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20ultimately%20determining%20that%20Cannon%20lacked%20the%20authority%20to%20assign%20a%20special%20master%20to%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20that%20Jack%20Smith%20moved%20for%20reconsideration%20of%20a%20Cannon%20order%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20the%20last%20time%2C%20it%20was%20ultimately%20taken%20on%20appeal%20to%20the%2011th%20Circuit%2C%20which%20sided%20with%20Smith%20and%20gave%20a%20'bench%20slap'%20to%20Cannon%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Lieb%2C%20a%20legal%20analyst%20and%20New%20York%20litigation%20attorney%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELieb%20added%20that%20there%20is%20no%20legal%20reason%20to%20unseal%20the%20witness%20list%20or%20their%20statements%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20it%20puts%20witnesses%20in%20danger%20and%20potentially%20causes%20them%20to%20refuse%20to%20testify%20further%20or%20change%20their%20testimony%20out%20of%20fear%2C%20which%20is%20the%20precise%20reason%20to%20seal.%20Plus%2C%20it%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin