ndia%20should%20hold%20a%20permanent%20seat%20on%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%20He%20believes%20that%20India's%20inclusion%20as%20a%20permanent%20member%20would%20greatly%20contribute%20to%20maintaining%20a%20balance%20and%20prioritizing%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20majority%20worldwide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frussian-ambassador-urges-un-reforms-and-indias-inclusion-in-security-council%2Farticleshow%2F107593331.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20Army%20Chief's%20%26quot%3BShow%20Maturity%26quot%3B%20Advice%20To%20Politicians%20Over%20Poll%20Results%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20army%20chief%20told%20feuding%20politicians%20Saturday%20to%20show%20%26quot%3Bmaturity%20and%20unity%26quot%3B%20after%20an%20election%20failed%20to%20produce%20a%20clear%20winner%2C%20leaving%20the%20military's%20favoured%20party%20having%20to%20cobble%20together%20a%20coalition%20in%20order%20to%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20faces%20days%20of%20political%20horse-trading%20after%20a%20strong%20performance%20by%20independent%20candidates%20loyal%20to%20jailed%20former%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan%20scuppered%20the%20chances%20of%20the%20army-backed%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20from%20winning%20a%20ruling%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan's%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20defied%20a%20months-long%20crackdown%20that%20crippled%20campaigning%20and%20forced%20candidates%20to%20run%20as%20independents%20with%20a%20combined%20showing%20that%20still%20challenged%20their%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20looms%20large%20over%20Pakistan's%20political%20landscape%2C%20with%20generals%20having%20run%20the%20country%20for%20nearly%20half%20its%20history%20since%20partition%20from%20India%20in%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElections%20are%20not%20a%20zero-sum%20competition%20of%20winning%20and%20losing%20but%20an%20exercise%20to%20determine%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20army%20chief%20General%20Syed%20Asim%20Munir%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20have%20reposed%20their%20combined%20trust%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20it%20is%20now%20incumbent%20upon%20all%20political%20parties%20to%20reciprocate%20the%20same%20with%20political%20maturity%20and%20unity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20nation%20needs%20stable%20hands%20and%20a%20healing%20touch%20to%20move%20on%20from%20the%20politics%20of%20anarchy%20and%20polarisation%20which%20does%20not%20suit%20a%20progressive%20country%20of%20250%20million%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EForced%20to%20cut%20deals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20long%20delays%20in%20results%20that%20prompted%20further%20allegations%20that%20the%20military%20establishment%20had%20engaged%20in%20vote-rigging%2C%20PML-N%20declared%20victory%20Friday%20as%20the%20party%20with%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20to%20form%20a%20government%2C%20the%20party%20founded%20by%20three-time%20former%20prime%20minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20cut%20deals%20with%20rivals%20and%20independents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20reports%20late%20Friday%20of%20leaders%20from%20several%20parties%20arriving%20in%20PML-N's%20power%20base%20of%20Lahore%20for%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20enough%20of%20a%20majority%20to%20run%20the%20government%20ourselves%2C%20therefore%20we%20invite%20the%20other%20parties%20and%20candidates%20who%20have%20been%20successful%20to%20work%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sharif%20said%20at%20his%20party%20headquarters%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20AI-generated%20video%20produced%20by%20PTI%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20was%20credited%20as%20claiming%20victory%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20independent%20sources%2C%20we%20were%20winning%20150%20national%20assembly%20seats%20before%20the%20rigging%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20message%20posted%20on%20his%20X%20account%2C%20which%20featured%20a%20genuine%20video%20clip%20of%20him%20from%20a%20year%20ago%20and%20an%20AI-generated%20voice-over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20slow%20counting%20process%20showed%20independents%20had%20won%20at%20least%20100%20seats%20--%2089%20of%20them%20loyal%20to%20Khan%20--%20by%20Saturday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPML-N%20took%2071%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20(PPP)%20snapped%20up%2054%2C%20with%2013%20of%20the%20elected%20266-seat%20National%20Assembly%20still%20to%20be%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinor%20parties%20shared%2027%20seats%20between%20them%20--%20including%20the%20Muttahida%20Qaumi%20Movement%20(MQM)%2C%20which%20took%2017%20--%20which%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20of%20great%20interest%20to%20PTI%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20PTI's%20independents%20join%20one%20of%20them%2C%20they%20can%20take%20a%20share%20of%20the%20further%2070%20unelected%20seats%20reserved%20for%20women%20and%20religious%20minorities%2C%20which%20are%20allocated%20according%20to%20party%20performance%20in%20the%20contested%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Recount%20our%20votes'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20seats%20won%20by%20Khan%20loyalists%20were%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20where%20police%20said%20at%20least%20two%20PTI%20supporters%20were%20killed%20Friday%20and%20more%20than%2020%20wounded%20when%20they%20protested%20against%20alleged%20vote-rigging%20in%20Shangla%20district%20--%20the%20first%20serious%20post-election%20violence%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20results%20have%20been%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20claimed%2028-year-old%20shopkeeper%20Muhammad%20Saleem%2C%20who%20joined%20around%202%2C000%20PTI%20supporters%20marching%20in%20Peshawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20should%20recount%20all%20of%20our%20votes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20Khan%20was%20barred%20from%20contesting%20the%20election%20after%20being%20handed%20several%20lengthy%20prison%20sentences%20in%20the%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20nationwide%20election%20day%20mobile%20telephone%20blackout%20and%20the%20slow%20counting%20of%20results%20led%20to%20suspicions%20the%20military%20establishment%20was%20influencing%20the%20process%20to%20ensure%20Sharif's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPTI%20as%20a%20party%20and%20political%20group%2C%20despite%20significant%20efforts%20by%20the%20civilian%20and%20military%20establishment%2C%20has%20held%20on%20to%20its%20vote%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bilal%20Gilani%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20polling%20group%20Gallup%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20that%20the%20military%20does%20not%20always%20get%20their%20way%20--%20that%20is%20the%20silver%20lining%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PPP%2C%20whose%20popularity%20is%20largely%20limited%20to%20its%20Sindh%20heartland%2C%20also%20did%20better%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PML-N%20and%20PPP%20joined%20forces%20with%20minor%20parties%20to%20boot%20Khan%20from%20office%20in%20April%202022%20after%20his%20PTI%20won%20a%20slender%20majority%20in%20the%202018%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20international%20cricketer%20then%20waged%20an%20unprecedented%20campaign%20of%20defiance%20against%20the%20military-led%20establishment%2C%20which%20originally%20backed%20his%20rise%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%20was%20convicted%20last%20week%20of%20treason%2C%20graft%20and%20having%20an%20un-Islamic%20marriage%20in%20three%20separate%20trials%20--%20among%20nearly%20200%20cases%20brought%20against%20him%20since%20being%2