20yet%20to%20be%20released.%20Nawaz%20Sharif's%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20took%2071%20seats%2C%20while%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari's%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20had%2054.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20independents'%20strong%20performance%20points%20to%20Khan's%20enduring%20popularity%20among%20the%20nation's%20129%20million%20registered%20voters%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20amid%20the%20fastest%20inflation%20in%20Asia.%20It%20also%20highlights%20public%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20status%20quo%20of%20Pakistani%20politics%2C%20represented%20by%20the%20parties%20of%20the%20Sharif%20and%20Bhutto%20clans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20PTI-backed%20independents%20are%20leading%20right%20now%20despite%20all%20the%20hurdles%20their%20party%20has%20faced%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election%20and%20in%20campaigning%20is%20a%20huge%20deal%20for%20Pakistan%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Madiha%20Afzal%2C%20a%20foreign%20policy%20fellow%20at%20Brookings%20Institution.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20shows%20the%20power%20of%20Khan's%20base%2C%20Pakistan's%20young%2C%20middle-class%20demographic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan's%20loyalists%20won%20most%20seats%20and%20have%20the%20first%20right%20to%20form%20a%20government%2C%20PTI%20party%20Chairman%20Gohar%20Ali%20Khan%20said%20at%20a%20briefing%20on%20Saturday%2C%20While%20all%20parties%20fell%20short%20of%20winning%20a%20majority%2C%20Sharif%20on%20Friday%20spoke%20to%20cheering%20crowds%20from%20his%20stronghold%20of%20Lahore%2C%20claiming%20victory%20and%20vowing%20to%20speak%20to%20Bhutto%20Zardari's%20PPP%20on%20forming%20an%20alliance%20to%20lead%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif's%20move%20may%20be%20welcomed%20by%20the%20powerful%20military%20which%20has%20clashed%20with%20Khan.%20Analysts%20say%20three-time%20former%20premier%20Sharif%2C%20who%20returned%20from%20exile%20in%20London%20last%20year%20and%20acquitted%20of%20corruption%20charges%2C%20had%20the%20blessings%20of%20the%20military%20for%20the%20top%20job.%20Bhutto%20Zardari%2C%2035%2C%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Benazir%20Bhutto%2C%20a%20former%20leader%20who%20was%20assassinated%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPakistan's%20diverse%20polity%20and%20pluralism%20will%20be%20well-represented%20by%20a%20unified%20government%20of%20all%20democratic%20forces%20imbibed%20with%20national%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20military%20said%20on%20Saturday.%20%E2%80%9CElections%20and%20democracy%20are%20means%20to%20serve%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20and%20not%20ends%20in%20themselves.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elections%20were%20marred%20by%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20remote%20provinces%20bordering%20Afghanistan%20that%20killed%20dozens.%20On%20polling%20day%2C%20Pakistan%20suspended%20mobile%20phone%20services%20nationwide%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20necessary%20for%20maintaining%20order.%20The%20US%20and%20European%20Union%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20mobile%20phone%20service%20suspension%20and%20polling%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20post-election%20instability%20and%20unrest%20would%20weigh%20on%20an%20economy%20already%20challenged%20on%20several%20fronts.%20Inflation%20is%20running%20at%2028%25%2C%20and%20the%20latest%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20bailout%20program%20is%20set%20to%20expire%20in%20March%2C%20suggesting%20the%20next%20leader%20will%20have%20to%20negotiate%20a%20new%20deal.%20He%20will%20also%20have%20to%20navigate%20complex%20ties%20with%20the%20US%20and%20China%2C%20rising%20domestic%20terrorism%20and%20tense%20relations%20with%20neighbors%20including%20India%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fm0no6tvk_pak-bloomberg-graphic_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Dcascade%2Cwidth%3D120