pitches%20and%20the%20opposing%20team%20suddenly%20comes%20with%20an%20aggressive%20mindset%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20more%20imaginative%2C%20which%20you%20expect%2C%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20asserted%20while%20talking%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cricketer-turned-commentator%20further%20stated%20that%20as%20Ashwin%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20touching%20the%20500%20mark%20so%20he%20has%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20bowl%20on%20flat%20pitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAshwin%20is%20standing%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20500%20wickets.%20So%20you%20expect%20that%20he%20will%20understand%20and%20manage%20all%20these%20things.%20However%2C%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20the%20Ravi%20of%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20hasn't%20risen%20in%20the%20series%20thus%20far.%20That's%20probably%20a%20combination%20of%20being%20used%20to%20mostly%20playing%20on%20turning%20pitches%20and%20Bazball%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20right-hand%20batter%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20on%20Saturday%20announced%20the%20squad%20for%20the%20remaining%20three%20Tests%20of%20the%20five-match%20series%20against%20England%2C%20with%20star%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20set%20to%20miss%20the%20remaining%20matches%20as%20well%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons.%20Virat%20had%20earlier%20missed%20the%20first%20two%20Tests.%20Now%2C%20his%20absence%20is%20extended%20to%20three%20more%20games.%20His%20last%20appearance%20came%20in%20the%20T20I%20series%20against%20Afghanistan%20earlier%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sarfaraz%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64385-sarfaraz-naushad-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESarfaraz%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rajat%20Patidar%5C%22%20href%3D%