eceived%20criticism.%20The%20NCP%20spokesperson%20Clyde%20Crasto%20called%20for%20strict%20action%20against%20Bangar%2C%20stating%20that%20he%20is%20a%20repeat%20offender%20and%20should%20be%20held%20accountable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22CHAITANYA%20MARPAKWAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fcontroversy-shiv-sena-mla-santosh-bangars-directive-to-schoolchildren-regarding-voting%2Farticleshow%2F107592899.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Peter%20Oloya%20-%20the%20Ugandan%20LRA%20child%20soldier%20who%20moulded%20a%20new%20future%20in%20art%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707615205000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FCB78%2Fproduction%2F_132588025_promo_uganda.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68217014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20Uganda's%20best%20sculptors%2C%20Peter%20Oloya%2C%20has%20used%20art%20to%20overcome%20his%20childhood%20abduction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68217014%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68217014.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68217014.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Harvard%20study%20says%20exercise%20not%20enough%20to%20balance%20heart%20attack%20risk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707615000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107585090%2Cimgsize-712270.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fharvard-study-exercise-alone-insufficient-to-counter-heart-attack-risk-from-sugary-drinks%2Farticleshow%2F107585105.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Excessive%20consumption%20of%20sugary%20drinks%20is%20linked%20to%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease.%20These%20beverages%2C%20high%20in%20added%20sugars%2C%20can%20contribute%20to%20weight%20gain%2C%20obesity%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20damage%20to%20blood%20vessels%2C%20raised%20blood%20sugar%20levels%2C%20inflammation%2C%20raised%20triglyceride%20levels%2C%20and%20cardiovascular%20disease.%20Public%20health%20recommendations%20include%20limiting%20intake%20of%20sugary%20drinks%20and%20lifestyle%20modifications.%20Heart%20disease%2C%20encompassing%20conditions%20like%20coronary%20artery%20disease%20and%20heart%20failure%2C%20stands%20as%20the%20foremost%20cause%20of%20death%20globally.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fharvard-study-exercise-alone-insufficient-to-counter-heart-attack-risk-from-sugary-drinks%2Farticleshow%2F107585105.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Election%20Commission's%20FAQs%20on%20EVMs%20Don't%20Really%20Address%20Major%20Design%20Deficiencies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10211621%2FEffect-2024-02-10T202212.238.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20new%20FAQs%20(frequently%20asked%20questions)%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20on%20January%2030%20and%20now%20superseded%20by%20another%20version%20on%20February%207%20is%20a%20very%20welcome%20step.%20Importantly%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20ECI%20has%20released%20at%20least%20some%20technical%20details%20about%20the%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs).%20The%20clarification%20that%20the%20trio%20of%20devices%20in%20the%20EVM%20uses%20RS-435%20serial%20communication%20brings%20clarity%20about%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20evident%20now%20that%20disconnecting%20the%20Voter%20Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20unit%20from%20the%20Control%20Unit%20(CU)%20is%20not%20a%20meredevice%20rearrangement.%20It%20will%20need%20redesign.%20And%20therefore%20the%20weakest%20part%20of%20the%20Electronic%20Election%20System%20(EES)%20ecosystem%20and%20the%20election%20process%20will%20remain%20the%20weakest%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20The%20diagram%20below%20clearly%20shows%20how%20the%20signal%20flows%20and%20that%20the%20electronic%20vote%20will%20not%20reach%20VVPAT%20from%20the%20Ballot%20Unit%20(BU)%20without%20first%20going%20to%20the%20CU%2C%20i.e.%20without%20the%20VVPAT-%20CU%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevm-election-commission-lok-sabha-faq-signal-kannan-gopinathan%5C%22%3EAhead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%2C%20EC%20Answers%20Longstanding%20Query%20on%20How%20EVMs%20Get%20Signals%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20said%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiaforum.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbringing-trust-electronic-elections-india%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20India%20Forum%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0on%20January%204%2C%20the%20use%20of%20EVM%20has%20changed%20the%20Indian%20election%20system%20to%20be%20an%20Electronic%20Election%20System%20(EES).%20In%20any%20system%2C%20it%20is%20not%20sufficient%20to%20scrutinise%20only%20one%20part%20of%20the%20system%2C%20irrespective%20of%20how%20important%20that%20part%20is.%20The%20system%20must%20hold%20its%20integrity%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20for%20being%20trustworthy.%20The%20EES%20being%20electronic%20now%20must%20demonstrate%20electronic%20integrity%20against%20physical%2C%20electronic%2C%20and%20digital%20threats.%20We%20need%20to%20scrutinise%20the%20EES%20on%20the%20combined%20criteria%20of%20physical%2C%20electronic%2C%20and%20digital%20integrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10205603%2Fevm.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10205603%2Fevm.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10205603%2Fevm-300x197.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10205603%2Fevm-1024x673.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696555%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22789%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20EES%20holistically%2C%20based%20on%20the%20material%20made%20available%20on%20their%20website%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%2C%20the%20following%20major%20design%20deficiencies%20continue%20to%20exist%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20EVM%20is%20not%20entirely%20location%20agnostic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20While%20the%20BU%20and%20CU%20are%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20is%20not%2C%20because%20it%20contains%20constituency-specific%20candidate%20data%2C%20uploaded%20only%20a%20few%20days%20before%20the%20polling.%20Location%20insensitivity%20is%20the%20first%20need%20for%20being%20fair%20and%20impartial.%20As%20such%20all%20the%202-stage%20randomization%20is%20not%20of%20much%20help%20when%20the%20computationally%20powerful%20component%20of%20the%20system%20is%20not%20location%20agnostic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20EVM%20is%20not%20entirely%20disconnected%20as%20claimed%20before.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20polling%20is%20ongoing%2C%20it%20is%20completely%20disconnected%3B%20but%20only%20a%20few%20days%20before%20polling%2C%20it%20indirectly%2C%20via%20the%20Symbol%20Upload%20Unit%20(SLU)%20and%20PC%2C%20connects%20to%20the%20internet%20i.e.%20to%20the%20ECI%20website%20to%20download%20constituency-specific%20data%2C%20to%20store%20candidate%20data.%20(answer%20to%20Q%2052)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20The%20claim%20that%20candidate%20data%20is%20only%20a%20bitmap%20(picture)%20is%20not%20the%20full%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20For%20the%20VVPAT%20to%20match%20the%20candidate%20data%20with%20the%20incoming%20numerical%20value%20of%20the%20electronic%20vote%2C%20the%20bitmap%20needs%20to%20be%20tagged%20with%20a%20numerical%20value%20or%20stored%20as%20elements%20of%20an%20array.%20It%20is%20unknown%20but%20entirely%20possible%20that%20the%20bitmap%20could%20be%20tagged%20with%20any%20additional%20value%20in%20either%20case.%20Such%20additional%20data%20can%20easily%20be%20used%20to%20alter%20the%20values%20returned%20by%20the%20VVPAT%20to%20the%20CU%2C%20and%20the%20way%20these%20responses%20are%20processed%20further%20by%20the%20CU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20The%20EVM%20is%20not%20a%20simple%20machine%20like%20a%20calculator%20as%20claimed%20before%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20While%20the%20BU%20and%20CU%20may%20be%20so%20(we%20must%20believe%20ECI%20%E2%80%93%20no%20details%20are%20made%20available%20as%20proof)%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20is%20certainly%20not.%20VVPAT%20has%20a%20program%20that%2C%20at%20a%20minimum%20has%20to%20process%20incoming%20numerical%20data%2C%20match%20it%20with%20the%20stored%20list%2C%20pass%20the%20bitmap%20image%20associated%20with%20the%20matched%20number%20to%20the%20printer%2C%20print%20the%20receipt%2C%20cut%20it%20and%20send%20a%20confirmation%20back%20to%20the%20CU.%20This%20is%20a%20fairly%20advanced%20set%20of%20operations%20than%20a%20mere%20Such%20a%20program%20could%20also%20be%20easily%20capable%20of%20counting%20the%20total%20number%20of%20votes%2C%20identify%20every%20%3Cem%3En%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eth%20%3C%2Fem%3Evote%2C%20provide%20more%20%E2%80%9Cmeaningful%E2%80%9D%20response%20to%20the%20CU%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20The%20VVPAT%20is%20not%20entirely%20One%20Time%20Programmable%20(OTP)%20as%20claimed%20before.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20a%20part%20of%20its%20memory%20is%20OTP%2C%20one%20part%20is%20ECI%20clearly%20said%20so%20in%20its%20response%20(%3Cu%3Eanswer%20to%20Q%2053%3C%2Fu%3E)%20in%20the%20new%20FAQ.%20Considering%20this%20revelation%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20must%20now%20be%20accepted%20as%20a%20seriously%20vulnerable%20device.%20Now%20it%20is%20unbelievably%20difficult%20for%20any%20digital%20system%20expert%20to%20defend%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20electronic%20vote%20in%20the%20CU%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20VVPAT%20receipt%2C%20more%20so%20because%20nothing%20is%20known%20about%20the%20program%20in%20the%20CU.Let%20us%20assume%20that%20the%20VVPAT%20responds%20with%20%E2%80%9CDone%20x%E2%80%9D%20in%20response%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9CPrint%20receipt%20for%20x%E2%80%9D%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fevms-can-be-manipulated-not-hacked-madhav-deshpande%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%20EVMs%20Can%20Be%20Manipulated%2C%20Not%20Hacked%20But%20Remedy%20is%20Simple%20and%20Inexpensive%3A%20Expert%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20hypothetical%20but%20plausible%20scenario%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9CPrint%20receipt%20for%203%E2%80%9D%20command%20from%20the%20CU%2C%20upon%20printing%20the%20receipt%20(bitmap%20image%20of%20the%20candidate%20name%2C%20party%20name%20and%20symbol)%20for%20candidate%20at%20position%203%2C%20if%20the%20VVPAT%20responds%20%E2%80%9CDone%203%2C5%E2%80%9D%20and%20if%20the%20CU%20program%20is%20written%20to%20recognise%20the%20x%2Cy%20part%20of%20the%20response%20as%20record%20the%20vote%20for%20x%20as%20vote%20for%20y%2C%20inaccurate%20registration%20of%20vote%20in%20the%20CU%20is%20possible%20even%20after%20accurate%20printing%20of%20the%20receipt%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20possible%20because%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ea.%20VVPAT%20has%20a%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Eb.%20This%20program%20is%20written%20specifically%20to%20receive%20a%20number%20from%20CU%20and%20match%20it%20with%20the%20number%20in%20the%20list%20uploaded%20by%20the%20SLU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ec.%20SLU%20must%20upload%20image%20data%20acquired%20from%20a%20PC%20connected%20to%20the%20internet.%20It%20is%20easily%20possible%20to%20add%20just%20one%20special%20byte%20to%20a%20specific%20bitmap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20may%20be%20capable%20of%20executing%20additional%20functions%20like%20keeping%20track%20of%20vote%20count%20etc.%20It%20may%20therefore%20take%20specific%20action%20in%20its%20response%20to%20such%20specific%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Considering%20the%20accepted%20vulnerability%20of%20the%20VVPAT%2C%20it%20becomes%20necessary%20to%20provide%20a%20recourse%20to%20every%20voter%20who%20complains%20of%20a%20VVPAT%20slip%20that%20does%20not%20match%20their%20choice%20of%20button%20press%3B%20because%20now%20with%20a%20programmable%20part%20of%20the%20VVPAT%2C%20it%20must%20be%20admitted%20that%20non-transparent%20transformation%20of%20the%20vote%20is%20possible%20even%20within%20the%20VVPAT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20VVPAT%20is%20a%20misnomer%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebecause%20it%20allows%20only%20view%2C%20not%20verification.%20The%20choice%20of%20rejection%20is%20a%20very%20crucial%20part%20of%20the%20verification%20process.%20Mere%20viewing%20is%20not%20verification.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20any%20authority%20verifies%20a%20document%2C%20the%20authority%20does%20not%20merely%20view%20it%2C%20it%20reserves%20the%20right%20to%20reject%20if%20the%20document%20is%20found%20incorrect.%20If%20a%20discrepancy%20is%20detected%2C%20does%20the%20voter%20have%20any%20agency%20to%20not%20just%20highlight%20the%20discrepancy%2C%20but%20mark%20the%20paper%20vote%20as%20incorrect%2C%20discard%20it%20and%20then%20cast%20a%20correct%20vote%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20rule%20sighted%20(Rule%2049)%2C%20if%20the%20voter%20fails%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20an%20unintended%20vote%20is%20cast%20for%20the%20NEXT%20test%20vote%2C%20they%20become%20a%20culprit%2C%20liable%20to%20criminal%20prosecution.%20Besides%20being%20tyrannical%2C%20this%20is%20also%20entirely%20unscientific.%20This%20is%20like%20denying%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20previously%20connected%20%E2%80%9Cwrong%20number%E2%80%9D%20from%20a%20phone%20if%20the%20next%20call%20connects%20correctly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668180%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20building%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40PIB_INDIA.%20November%205%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20Answer%20to%20Q%2049%20says%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20DRE%20produces%20a%20voter%20verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail%2C%20it%20is%20software%20%E2%80%9D%20What%20is%20the%20basis%20for%20this%20definition%3F%20No%20reference%20is%20cited.%20The%20principle%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.realworldevoting.com%2Ffiles%2FChapter1.pdf)%5C%22%3Esoftware%20independence%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20was%20introduced%20by%20Wack%20and%20Rivest%20and%20according%20to%20its%20application%20to%20a%20voting%20system%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20voting%20system%20is%20software-independent%20if%20an%20(undetected)%20change%20or%20error%20in%20its%20software%20cannot%20cause%20an%20undetectable%20change%20or%20error%20in%20an%20election%20outcome.%E2%80%9D%20Software%20System%E2%80%9D%20in%20this%20definition%20includes%20both%20program%20and%20data%20constants.%20Since%20undetected%20data%20constants%20(like%20a%20*%20against%20an%20image%20or%20an%20%3Cem%3Ex%2Cy%20%3C%2Fem%3Estyled%20response%20as%20mentioned%20in%20%E2%80%9C5%E2%80%9D%20above)%20may%20be%20processed%20by%20the%20unknown%20program%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20and%20CU%20to%20cause%20error%20in%20the%20election%20outcome%2C%20undetected%20change%20can%20cause%20a%20detectable%20change%20in%20the%20election%20outcome%20and%20therefore%20the%20test%20for%20software%20independence%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20%2B%20CU%20fails%20even%20on%20theoretical%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20The%20answer%20to%20Question%2037%20talks%20about%20digital%20certificates%20and%20public%20key%20encryption%20for%20authentication.%20However%2C%20merely%20being%20from%20an%20authentic%20group%20is%20insufficient%20here.%20Unique%20pairing%20is%20necessary%20to%20eliminate%20an%20authentic%20but%20illegitimate%20%2F%20replacement%20unit%20being%20used.%20Authentication%20does%20not%20address%20the%20replacement%20of%20one%20unit%20by%20another.%20That%20can%20be%20done%20only%20by%20pairing.%20And%20there%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20pairing.%20While%20the%20entire%20pool%20of%20the%20BUs%2C%20VVPATs%20and%20CUs%20carries%20electronic%20certificates%20of%20authentication%20from%20the%20time%20of%20manufacture%3B%20individual%20BU%2C%20VVPAT%20and%20CU%20are%20not%20uniquely%20paired%20on%20the%20polling%20day%2C%20nor%20is%20the%20pairing%20verified%20on%20the%20counting%20day.%20This%20leaves%20ample%20scope%20for%20the%20CU%20used%20for%20polling%20to%20be%20replaced%20by%20another%20authentic%20CU%20stuffed%20with%20spurious%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20digital%20certificate%20is%20akin%20to%20an%20entry%20pass%20issued%20to%20the%20participants%20of%20a%20close-group%20meeting.%20The%20door%20keeper%20allows%20entry%20to%20the%20pass%20holder%20without%20knowing%20their%20identity.%20This%20allows%20person%20B%20to%20enter%20in%20place%20of%20person%20A%20so%20long%20as%20B%20carries%20the%20pass.%20In%20every%20high-security%20environment%2C%20a%20unique%20identification%20for%20every%20member%20is%20not%20just%20necessary%2C%20but%20it%20must%20be%20established%20and%20verified%2C%20as%20we%20experience%20it%20at%20the%20airport%20entry.%20A%20boarding%20pass%20is%20necessary%20but%20for%20sufficiency%2C%20we%20need%20a%20government-issued%20identifier%20to%20uniquely%20establish%20our%20identity.%20Person%20B%20cannot%20enter%20the%20airport%20using%20person%20A%E2%80%99s%20boarding%20pass.%20This%20simple%20example%20of%20routinely%20established%20security%20more%20than%20highlights%20the%20need%20for%20unique%20identification%20as%20a%20necessary%20and%20sufficient%20condition%20in%20every%20secure%20system.%20Only%20the%20act%20of%20pairing%20all%20three%20components%20of%20the%20EVM%20with%20a%20unique%20identifier%20for%20each%20passes%20this%20necessary%20and%20sufficient%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fz5Y6z29El3I%3Fsi%3DuoBuR47dVV1-n0Uu%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20the%20disconnected%20and%20dispersed%20nature%20of%20the%20EVM%20unit%2C%20at%20least%20one%20dynamic%20component%20must%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20unique%20identifier.%20Such%20a%20dynamic%20component%20is%20easily%20available%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20date%20and%20time%20of%20pairing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E10.%20EVM%E2%80%99s%20location%20is%20not%20tracked%20every%20moment%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20The%20less%20harmful%20fall-out%20of%20this%20laxity%20in%20surveillance%20is%20these%20units%20being%20stolen%20by%20anti-social%20elements%20and%20their%20following%20misuse%20in%20some%20constituencies.%20The%20more%20serious%20fall-out%20is%20a%20possible%20mass-scale%20rigging%20by%20unfriendly%20countries%20to%20sabotage%20the%20entire%20election.%20This%20must%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20national%20threat.%20In%20a%20country%20that%20talks%20of%20GPS%20tagging%20every%20car%20so%20that%20toll%20booths%20are%20eliminated%2C%20not%20tagging%20EVMs%20with%20GPS%20is%20not%20just%20baffling%2C%20it%20shows%20total%20disregard%20for%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E11.%20The%20entire%20EVM%20documentation%20(FAQ)%20has%20no%20disaster%20recovery%20(DR)%20implementation%2C%20or%20even%20a%20Considering%20that%20the%20outcome%20of%20elections%20decides%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20nation%20for%20half%20a%20decade%2C%20and%20that%20accidents%20are%20not%20too%20rare%20even%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20absence%20of%20DR%20is%20entirely%20unacceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%20immediate%2C%20major%2C%20serious%2C%20discomforting%20deficiencies%20in%20the%20EES%20itself%2C%20I%20notice%20that%20every%20voter%20now%20has%20two%20copies%20of%20votes%3A%20one%20in%20the%20form%20of%20printed%20paper%20slip%20via%20VVPAT%20and%20the%20other%20in%20the%20form%20of%20electronic%20vote%20stored%20in%20the%20CU.%20Kannan%20Gopinathan%20has%20been%20asking%20a%20fundamental%20question%20in%20this%20regard.%20It%20needs%20to%20be%20answered%20by%20not%20just%20the%20ECI%2C%20but%20also%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%20The%20question%20is%3A%20which%20is%20the%20real%20vote%3F%20The%20one%20that%20the%20voter%20has%20seen%20though%20not%20actively%20verified%20or%20the%20one%20that%20is%20neither%20seen%20nor%20verified%20by%20the%20voter%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20the%20volume%20of%20the%20task%20of%20making%20design%20changes%20and%20implementing%20them%20across%20the%20EVMs%2C%20the%20time%20may%20be%20inadequate%20before%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20However%2C%20looking%20at%20the%20real%20and%20existential%20possibilities%20of%20manipulation%20that%20are%20open%20as%20now%20seen%20even%20more%20after%20the%20new%20information%20in%20the%20FAQ%2C%20the%20most%20appropriate%20action%20for%20the%20ECI%20would%20be%20to%20adopt%20a%20%E2%80%9Chybrid%20model%E2%80%9D%20by%20using%20the%20EVM%20to%20print%20the%20slip%20and%20manually%20counting%20100%25%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20receipts%20(like%20paper%20ballots)%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20manual%20counting%20effort%20may%20take%20an%20additional%20few%20days%2C%20but%20then%20those%20who%20win%2C%20stay%20in%20power%20for%20five%20years.%20I%20am%20sure%20a%20three-day%20delay%20is%20worth%20the%20wait%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20Indian%20democracy.%20The%20solutions%20to%20address%20the%20problems%20discussed%20above%20should%20be%20taken%20up%20as%20a%20year-long%20project%20and%20implemented%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMadhav%20Deshpande%20is%20a%20former%20CEO%20of%20Tulip%20Software%20and%20a%20former%20consultant%20to%20the%20Obama%20administration%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20He%20is%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20foremost%20experts%20on%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs).%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707614948000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10211621%2FEffect-2024-02-10T202212.238.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-commissions-faqs-on-evms-dont-really-address-major-design-deficiencies%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20use%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20has%20changed%20the%20Indian%20election%20system%20to%20be%20an%20Electronic%20Election%20System%20(EES).%20In%20any%20system%2C%20it%20is%20not%20sufficient%20to%20scrutinise%20only%20one%20part%20of%20the%20system%2C%20irrespective%20of%20how%20important%20that%20part%20is.%20The%20system%20must%20hold%20its%20integrity%20as%20a%20whole%20for%20being%20trustworthy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felection-commissions-faqs-on-evms-dont-really-address-major-design-deficiencies%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jeff%20Bezos%20just%20sold%20off%20%242%20billion%20in%20Amazon%20shares%20in%20what%20could%20be%20a%20strategy%20to%20make%20him%20the%20richest%20man%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeff%20Bezos%20(left)%20smirks%20in%20a%20composite%20image%20next%20to%20Elon%20Musk%20%5Cn(right)%20grimacing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c7fb99917a1dae024547e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBefore%20this%20week's%20sale%20of%20Amazon%20stock%2C%20Jeff%20Bezos'%20net%20worth%20was%20only%20%245%20billion%20behind%20Elon%20Musk's%20%24200%20billion%20fortune%2C%20putting%20the%20title%20of%20%26quot%3Bworld's%20richest%20man%26quot%3B%20within%20reach.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20week%20Jeff%20Bezos%20sold%2012%20million%20shares%20of%20Amazon%20stock%2C%20netting%20about%20%242%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20Bezos'%20first%20major%20sale%20of%20stock%20in%20the%20company%20since%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20puts%20Bezos'%20within%20reach%20of%20overtaking%20Elon%20Musk%20as%20the%20world's%20richest%20man.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-life-career-education%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeff%20Bezos%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethis%20week%20unloaded%2012%20million%20shares%20of%20Amazon%20stock%2C%20netting%20him%20about%20%242%20billion%20in%20a%20strategic%20move%20that%20may%20position%20him%20to%20once%20again%20claim%20the%20title%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Fbusiness%2Fnews%2Ftop-10-richest-people-in-the-world%2Farticleshow%2F74415117.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworld's%20richest%20man%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20was%20in%20keeping%20with%20a%20plan%20announced%20by%20the%20company%20earlier%20in%20February%20for%20Bezos%20to%20sell%20off%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-elon-musk-net-worth-wealth-amazon-tesla-stock-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E50%20million%20shares%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20valued%20at%20roughly%20%248.5%20billion%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20owned%20988%20million%20shares%2C%20just%20shy%20of%2010%25%20of%20Amazon%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20December%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company's%202023%20proxy%20statement%2C%20with%20his%20entire%20stake%20worth%20about%20%24168%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20sharp%20rise%20in%20Amazon's%20stock%20this%20year%20has%20led%20to%20a%20%2422.6%20billion%20rise%20in%20the%20company's%20founder%20and%20executive%20chairman's%20estimated%20wealth%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fbillionaires%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBloomberg%20Billionaires%20Index%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fbillionaires%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20surge%20has%20propelled%20Bezos%20into%20second%20place%20on%20the%20world's%20richest%20people%20list%2C%20with%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%24200%20billion%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20exact%20motive%20behind%20Bezos'%20decision%20to%20offload%20shares%20is%20unknown%2C%20the%20massive%20sale%20does%20shrink%20the%20gap%20between%20his%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%20net%20worth%2C%20positioning%20Bezos%20to%20overtake%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%20in%20the%20rankings%20of%20the%20world's%20richest%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%20week's%20sale%20of%20Amazon%20stock%2C%20Bezos'%20net%20worth%20was%20only%20%245%20billion%20behind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-net-worth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk's%20%24200%20billion%20fortune%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20putting%20the%20title%20of%20%231%20billionaire%20well%20within%20reach.%20Musk's%20net%20worth%20rose%20to%20%24209%20billion%20in%20the%20days%20since%2C%20per%20Bloomberg's%20Billionaires%20Index%2C%20but%20the%20race%20for%20Bezos%20to%20catch%20up%20to%20Musk%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20first%20became%20the%20richest%20person%20in%20the%20world%20in%202017%2C%20overtaking%20Bill%20Gates.%20The%20pair%20traded%20off%20the%20title%20through%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20but%20Bezos%20held%20the%20position%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20man%20in%20the%20world%20from%202018%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethrough%202021%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fforbeswealthteam%2Farticle%2Fthe-top-ten-richest-people-in-the-world%2F%3Fsh%3D172e050a54dc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E'%20list%20of%20the%20world's%20billionaires%2C%20when%20Musk%20overtook%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Bezos'%20wealth%20has%20surged%20this%20year%2C%20Musk's%20has%20fallen%20by%20%2429%20billion%2C%20due%20in%20part%20to%20a%2027%25%20plunge%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Estock%20prompted%20by%20weaker-than-expected%20growth%20for%20the%20electric%20car%20company%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20Delaware%20judge's%20January%2030%20ruling%20that%20voided%2