d.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20tastes%20are%20not%20normal%20in%20bullfighting.%20Both%20politically%20and%20sexually.%20I%20am%20pansexual%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20said%20he%20wasn't%20sure%20how%20people%20in%20the%20bullrings%20would%20react%20to%20the%20news%2C%20he%20clarified%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20care%20what%20other%20people%20think.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20later%20interview%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68226508%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Alcalde%20said%20he%20had%20been%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20the%20response%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20are%20accepting%20it%20and%20in%20the%20best%20way%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20open%20a%20meeting%20place%20for%20bullfighting%20fans%20in%20Madrid's%20LGBTQ%2B%20neighborhood%20of%20Chueca%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlcalde%20is%20also%20hoping%20that%20his%20decision%20to%20come%20out%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20others%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20a%20sport%20that%20has%20traditionally%20been%20associated%20with%20%26quot%3Bmachismo%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20masculine%20pride%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Spanish%20conservatism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESupporters%20claim%20that%20bullfighting%20is%20an%20art%20form%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221183%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bull%20charges%20at%20a%20red%20cape%20held%20by%20a%20matador%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63dd8803e33c4000193aeead%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22787%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20bull%20and%20matador%20in%20a%20bullring%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBullfighting%20has%20long%20been%20a%20controversial%20topic%20both%20in%20Spain%20and%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20has%20been%20banned%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20the%20blood%20sport%20remains%20legal%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20Spain%2C%20according%20to%20the%20animal%20welfare%20organization%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsi.org%2Fnews-resources%2Fbullfighting%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAlthough%2520legal%2520in%2520Spain%252C%2520some%2C%252C%2520Peru%252C%2520and%2520Ecuador).%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHumane%20Society%20International%3C%2Fa%3E%20(HSI).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20popularity%20for%20bullfighting%20has%20declined%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn7YDa-m8vvc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethousands%20have%20turned%20out%20at%20rallies%3C%2Fa%3E%20demanding%20an%20end%20to%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20for%20the%20Ethical%20Treatment%20of%20Animals%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.peta.org%2Fissues%2Fanimals-in-entertainment%2Fanimals-used-entertainment-factsheets%2Fbullfighting-tradition-tragedy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPETA%3C%2Fa%3E)%20says%20that%20thousands%20of%20bulls%20die%20every%20year%20in%20bullfights%2C%20which%20it%20notes%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Binaccurate%20term%26quot%3B%20for%20an%20event%20that%20involves%20pitting%20a%20%26quot%3Bnimble%2C%20sword-wielding%20matador%26quot%3B%20against%20a%20%26quot%3Bconfused%2C%20maimed%2C%20psychologically%20tormented%2C%20and%20physically%20debilitated%20animal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupporters%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20claim%20that%20bullfighting%20is%20an%20art%20form%20that%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20Spanish%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlcalde%20is%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20had%20to%20live%20another%20life%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20mind%20being%20a%20brave%20bull%20and%20dying%20like%20a%20brave%20bull%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessin