lim%3F%E2%80%9D%20inquired%20one%20of%20the%20youths.%20Before%20I%20could%20respond%2C%20another%20interjected%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20it%20even%20a%20question%20worth%20asking%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20they%20vacated%20the%20lower%20berth%20and%20disembarked%20at%20Rewari%2C%20another%20passenger%2C%20who%20introduced%20himself%20as%20a%20court%20clerk%20from%20Jaipur%2C%20descended%20from%20the%20upper%20berth%20and%20sat%20facing%20me.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20youths%20are%20being%20swayed%20by%20a%20poisonous%20wind.%20They%20show%20no%20concern%20for%20jobs%20or%20careers.%20They%20will%20be%20doomed%20if%20Modi%20returns%20to%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarked%20solemnly.%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20words%20were%20in%20contrast%20to%20those%20of%20a%20banker%20in%20a%20black%20suit%20and%20matching%20tie%20whom%20I%20met%20at%20a%20wedding%20party%20in%20Jodhpur%2C%20loading%20a%20variety%20of%20savouries%20onto%20his%20plate.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20items%20are%20associated%20with%20Modi%20ji%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarked%2C%20pointing%20at%20dhoklas.%20He%20smiled%20and%20murmured%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram.%E2%80%9D%20Another%20guest%20chimed%20in%2C%20%E2%80%9CModi%20has%20announced%20he%20will%20win%20400%20seats!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20bustling%20Paharganj%20area%20of%20New%20Delhi%2C%20taxi%20driver%20Sukhvinder%20seethed%20with%20anger%20toward%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20%E2%80%9CModi%E2%80%99s%20guarantees%E2%80%A6it%E2%80%99s%20all%20a%20big%20farce%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20exclaimed.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20made%20our%20lives%20hell.%20We%E2%80%99re%20losing%20jobs%2C%20and%20the%20prices%20of%20essential%20commodities%20are%20skyrocketing.%E2%80%9D%20Sukhvinder%20recalled%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20enforce%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftrucker-protests-are-another-instance-of-the-success-of-street-politics%5C%22%3Edraconian%20law%20against%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20only%20withdrawn%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20he%20returns%20to%20power%2C%20he%E2%80%99ll%20bring%20back%20that%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20jailed%20Satendar%20Jain%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20%5BAam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leaders%20and%20Delhi%20ministers%5D%2C%20and%20he%20will%20do%20the%20same%20with%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20%5BDelhi%20chief%20minister%5D.%20Are%20he%20and%20his%20party%20men%20honest%20while%20all%20others%20are%20corrupt%3F%20Enough%20is%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sukhvinder%20declared%20passionately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CManmohan%20Singh%20was%20the%20best%20prime%20minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sukhvinder%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Shatrughan%2C%20another%20taxi%20driver%20from%20Ayodhya%2C%20working%20in%20Delhi%2C%20held%20a%20contrasting%20view.%20He%20greeted%20me%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CModi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20built%20the%20house%20for%20Ram.%20We%2C%20the%20dwellers%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20are%20happy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20narrate%20how%20businessmen%20had%20distributed%20flags%20free%20of%20cost%20among%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERam%20Rajya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahendra%20Nath%20Ojha%2C%20a%20former%20professor%20of%20Hindi%20at%20the%20Delhi%20University%20and%20former%20civil%20servant%20who%20was%20contemporary%20of%20the%20Union%20finance%20minister%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20at%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20offered%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20the%20contrasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Ramrajya%20is%20an%20anti-thesis%20to%20what%20Valmiki%2C%20Tulsidas%20and%20other%20saints%20propounded%20in%20their%20epics%20on%20Ram.%20Ramrajya%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%E2%80%99s%20portrayal%20of%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%20Ram%20symbolises%20struggle%2C%20sacrifice%2C%20justice%2C%20equality%20and%20everything%20about%20how%20a%20human%20being%20should%20live%20like%20in%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOjha%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20poet%20and%20an%20expert%20on%20Bhakti%20literature%2C%20quoted%20a%20verse%20from%20Tulsidas%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EJau%20aniti%20kachhu%20bhakhav%20bhai%2C%20tau%20mohi%20barajo%20bhai%20bisrai.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20see%20any%20wrongdoing%2C%20convey%20it%20to%20me%20without%20any%20fear%2C%20it%20says.%20In%20this%20verse%2C%20Ram%2C%20as%20a%20king%2C%20advises%20his%20subjects%20never%20to%20fear%20injustice%20and%20to%20inform%20him%20about%20all%20wrongs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20Indian%20society%20has%20changed%20with%20the%20adoption%20of%20radical%20Hindutva%20over%20values%20of%20inclusion%2C%20tolerance%2C%20and%20accommodation%2C%20Ojha%20responded%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20society%20is%20inherently%20inclusive%20and%20accommodative.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20adopted%20at%20Independence%20embodies%20the%20pluralism%20and%20spirit%20of%20co-existence%20that%20has%20been%20the%20hallmark%20of%20our%20society%20since%20time%20immemorial.%20From%20Valmiki%20to%20Tulsidas%2C%20and%20from%20Vedvyas%20to%20Kabir%2C%20you%20will%20find%20threads%20of%20unity%20in%20diversity.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20is%20using%20religion%20for%20political%20gains.%20But%20it%20is%20simply%20a%20dark%20spell%2C%20like%20a%20storm.%20Make%20no%20mistake%2C%20no%20storm%20lasts%20forever.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707571809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09184841%2FUntitled-design-8-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunali