idealism%20of%20independent%20India%20was%20unravelling%20before%20Karnad%E2%80%99s%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20creative%20response%20to%20these%20events%20was%20his%201989%20play%2C%20%3Cem%3ETal%C3%A9%20Danda%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Beheadin%3C%2Fem%3Eg.%20It%20is%20a%20story%20of%20the%20spiritual%2C%20social%2C%20and%20literary%20movement%20of%20Basavanna%E2%80%99s%20sharanas%20in%20medieval%20Karnataka%20and%20the%20undoing%20of%20this%20radically%20egalitarian%20movement%20in%20a%20bloody%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20394px)%2085vw%2C%20394px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10152512%2Funnamed.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22394%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10152512%2Funnamed.jpg%20394w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10152512%2Funnamed-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10152512%2Funnamed-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696509%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22394%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERakt%20Kalyan%2C%20directed%20by%20Sunil%20Shanbag%2C%20staged%20by%20The%20Drama%20School%2C%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETal%C3%A9%20Danda%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20set%20in%20the%201100s.%20King%20Bijjala%20II%20reigns%20and%20the%20city%20of%20Kalyana%20faces%20a%20social%20crisis.%20A%20Brahmin%20city%20girl%20wishes%20to%20marry%20a%20boy%20from%20a%20lower%20caste.%20Together%2C%20the%20lovers%20turn%20to%20Basavanna%2C%20a%20poet-saint%20leading%20a%20movement%20that%20opposes%20all%20that%20orthodox%20Hinduism%20stands%20for%3A%20idolatry%2C%20temple%20worship%2C%20and%20the%20caste%20system.%20He%20holds%20equality%20and%20non-violence%20above%20all%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20playtext%20of%20%3Cem%3ETal%C3%