p%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20many%20CCS%20members%20were%20curious%20to%20know%20why%20so%20much%20trouble%20is%20being%20taken%20when%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20already%20declared%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20win%20more%20than%20370%20seats%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Big%20Boss%20Proxy%3A%20%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20where%20nobody%20has%20ever%20been%20able%20to%20de-code%20the%20sheer%20street-smartness%20of%20the%20Boss%E2%80%99%20grand%20strategy.%20You%20create%20this%20massive%20perception%2C%20with%20those%20silly%20Pavlovian%20dogs%20in%20the%20media%20echoing%20the%20inevitability%20of%20a%20Modi%20wave.%20They%20fall%20over%20one%20another%20in%20serenading%20this%20or%20that%20master-stroke%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20They%20openly%20permit%20themselves%20to%20say%20how%20clever%20and%20brilliant%20our%20man%20is%3B%20and%2C%20by%20the%20same%20token%2C%20they%20have%20good%20reason%20to%20find%20the%20opposition%20in%20a%20disarray.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHere%20is%20the%20secret%20%5Bnot%20to%20be%20whispered%20outside%20this%20room%5D%3A%20once%20the%20overwhelming%20perception%20of%20an%20unstoppable%20Modi%20wave%20gets%20cast%20in%20stone%2C%20then%20we%20have%20practically%20fixed%20the%20%E2%80%98mood%20of%20the%20nation.%E2%80%99%20And%20then%20nobody%20will%20want%20to%20call%20out%20our%20%E2%80%9Cmisuse%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20system%20%5Bwith%20due%20apologies%20to%20Justice%20Sinha%2C%20of%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20case%20fame%5D.%20Even%20the%20courts%20will%20look%20the%20other%20way%2C%20what%20to%20talk%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20My%20own%20gut%20feeling%20is%20that%20after%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9C370%E2%80%9D%20declaration%2C%20this%20business%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20will%20remain%20on%20the%20judicial%20back-burner%20or%20even%20be%20decided%20in%20our%20favour.%20It%20is%20the%20law%20of%20the%20power%20