ur%20man%20is%3B%20and%2C%20by%20the%20same%20token%2C%20they%20have%20good%20reason%20to%20find%20the%20opposition%20in%20a%20disarray.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHere%20is%20the%20secret%20%5Bnot%20to%20be%20whispered%20outside%20this%20room%5D%3A%20once%20the%20overwhelming%20perception%20of%20an%20unstoppable%20Modi%20wave%20gets%20cast%20in%20stone%2C%20then%20we%20have%20practically%20fixed%20the%20%E2%80%98mood%20of%20the%20nation.%E2%80%99%20And%20then%20nobody%20will%20want%20to%20call%20out%20our%20%E2%80%9Cmisuse%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20system%20%5Bwith%20due%20apologies%20to%20Justice%20Sinha%2C%20of%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20case%20fame%5D.%20Even%20the%20courts%20will%20look%20the%20other%20way%2C%20what%20to%20talk%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20My%20own%20gut%20feeling%20is%20that%20after%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9C370%E2%80%9D%20declaration%2C%20this%20business%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20will%20remain%20on%20the%20judicial%20back-burner%20or%20even%20be%20decided%20in%20our%20favour.%20It%20is%20the%20law%20of%20the%20power%20jungle%20that%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20take%20a%20%3Cem%3Epanga%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20a%20sure%20%E2%80%98winner%E2%80%99.%20And%20the%20cherry%20on%20the%20cake%20will%20be%20that%20the%20media%20will%20pat%20itself%20on%20the%20back%20for%20being%20so%20precise%20and%20accurate%20in%20predicting%20a%20Modi%20wave.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CCS%20was%20once%20again%20in%20awe%20of%20the%20unending%20tricks%20the%20Big%20Boss%20has%20up%20his%20sleeve.%20They%20all%20felt%20it%20was%20time%20that%20he%20should%20give%20himself%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAtmanirbhar%20is%20the%20pen-name%20of%20an%20aspiring%20satirist%2C%20who%20irregularly%20contributes%20a%20column%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fbyline%2Fatmanirbhar%5C%22%3EFrom%20the%20Vis