9616.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-5-1707479616-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-5-1707479616-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-5-1707479616-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fsaffron-5-1707479616-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341331%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAastha%20and%20Vaibhav%20Patel%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vaibhav%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20said%20that%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%205%2C707%20hectares%20of%20land%20under%20saffron%20cultivation%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20more%20than%2090%20percent%20is%20in%20the%20Pampore%20tehsil%20of%20Pulwama%20district%20in%20South%20Kashmir.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20Valley%20rejoiced%20as%20the%20GI%20tag%20was%20given%20to%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20making%20it%20illegal%20for%20someone%20outside%20the%20valley%20to%20make%20and%20sell%20a%20similar%20product%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Kashmiri%20saffron%E2%80%99%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saffron%20grown%20in%20the%20Valley%20is%20of%20three%20types%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Lachha%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20variety%20where%20stigmas%20just%20separated%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329424%2Fludhiana-woman-grows-200-plants-in-terrace-garden-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20flowers%20are%20dried%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20further%20processing%3B%20%E2%80%98Mongra%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20variety%20where%20stigmas%20are%20detached%20from%20the%20flower%2C%20dried%20in%20the%20sun%2C%20and%20processed%20traditionally%3B%20and%20%E2%80%98Guchhi%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20which%20also%20does%20not%20involve%20the%20stigmas%20being%20processed.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20dried%20and%20joined%20in%20a%20bundle%20tied%20with%20a%20cloth%20thread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20that%20the%20Patels%20are%20growing%20is%20the%20second%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20harvest%20was%20an%20experiment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaibhav%20emphasises.%20But%20lucrative%20all%20the%20same.%20Each%20gram%20of%20the%20red%20threads%20fetched%20the%20couple%20Rs%20700.%20As%20for%20the%20road%20ahead%2C%20they%20are%20confident%20they%20can%20expand%20sales%20implementing%20the%20learnings%20of%20the%20previous%20harvest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707485452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_0318_11zon-1707478888.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20to%20grow%20saffron%20at%20home%3F%20Vaibhav%20Patel%20and%20Aastha%20Maheshwari%20Patel%20have%20transformed%20their%20Vadodara%20home%20into%20a%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20haven%2C%20defying%20geographical%20norms.%20They%20share%20insights%20into%20the%20intricate%20process%20of%20growing%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20expensive%20spice%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Search%20for%20runner%20and%20mum-of-three%20who%20vanished%20six%20days%20ago%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707484680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F70x70%2Fskynews-samantha-murphy-victoria-police_6449609.jpg%3F20240209123645%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Faustralia-victoria-police-search-for-missing-runner-and-mother-of-three-who-vanished-six-days-ago-13067431%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Specialist%20investigators%20in%20Australia%