und%20that%20while%20working%20with%20one%20of%20his%20PhD%20objectives%20%E2%80%94%20where%20he%20was%20focusing%20on%20the%20development%20of%20an%20advanced%20bio-oxidation%20system%20for%20water%20remediation%20%E2%80%94%20he%20realised%20that%20there%20were%20very%20limited%20multiparametric%20devices%20available%20to%20promptly%20check%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20in%20real-time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20motivated%20me%20to%20channel%20my%20efforts%20into%20creating%20a%20solution%20that%20would%20not%20only%20aid%20in%20my%20research%20but%20also%20serve%20the%20broader%20community%20by%20providing%20an%20affordable%2C%20real-time%2C%20and%20multi-parametric%20water%20quality%20monitoring%20tool%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20it%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20features%20of%20this%20IoT-enabled%20real-time%20water%20monitoring%20system%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%20Integrated%20GPS%3A%20Enables%20precise%20location%20tracking%20of%20water%20quality%20metrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%20Diverse%20Sensors%3A%20Measures%20turbidity%2C%20Total%20Dissolved%20Solids%20(TDS)%2C%20oxygen%20levels%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20pressure%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20water%20quality%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%20ESP32%20Microprocessor%3A%20Powers%20the%20device%20with%20efficient%20processing%20and%20communication%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%20Hybrid%20Power%20System%3A%20Ensures%20adaptability%20to%20different%20environments%2C%20reducing%20reliance%20on%20a%20single%20power%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%20AI%20Integration%3A%20Designed%20to%20incorporate%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20enhancing%20data%20analysis%20and%20predictive%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%97%8F%20Advanced%20Data%20Retrieval%3A%20Streamlines%20access%20to%20collected%20data%20for%20user-friendly%20interactions%20with%20various%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Satyam%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20R-SAM-PRO%20is%20based%20on%20a%20microprocessor.%20It%20has%20a%20set%20of%20sensors%20for%20TDS%20(total%20dissolved%20solids)%2C%20turbidity%2C%20dissolved%20oxygen%2C%20GPS%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20pressure%2C%20alongside%20an%20additional%20sensor%20for%20component%20area%20humidity%20monitoring.%20Upon%20activation%2C%20these%20sensors%20relay%20data%20to%20the%20microprocessor%2C%20which%20processes%20and%20securely%20transmits%20it%20to%20a%20real-time%20database.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsers%20can%20access%20this%20data%20through%20a%20user-friendly%20console%2C%20visualising%20it%20in%20graphical%20or%20tabular%20formats%20and%20tracking%20the%20sensor%E2%80%99s%20location.%20The%20device%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Chybrid%20power%20management%20system%E2%80%9D%20ensures%20its%20operational%20longevity%20across%20day%20and%20night%20cycles%2C%20making%20it%20versatile%20for%20various%20applications%2C%20from%20municipal%20water%20monitoring%20to%20industrial%20wastewater%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20work%20is%20protected%20by%20a%20patent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20further%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20device%20leverages%20the%20IoT%20for%20seamless%20communication%20between%20devices%20and%20cloud-based%20databases%2C%20significantly%20enhancing%20its%20utility%20and%20accessibility.%20The%20vast%20data%20collected%20can%20be%20used%20to%20train%20AI%20models%20to%20predict%20water%20quality%20variations%2C%20providing%20valuable%20insights%20for%20both%20local%20populations%20and%20industrial%20settings.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20IoT%20and%20AI%20technologies%20advance%2C%20they%20promise%20to%20revolutionise%20our%20understanding%20and%20management%20of%20water%20resources%20and%20sanitation.%20For%20example%2C%20based%20on%20trained%20data%20it%20can%20predict%20pre%20and%20post-monsoon%20water%20parameters%20range%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IIT%20Guwahati%20PhD%20scholar%20develops%20IoT-enabled%20water%20quality%20measuring%20device%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIIT-G-Water-Quality-Monitoring-Device-Presentation-1707316174-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341096%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESatyam%20presenting%20his%20innovation%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20this%20device%20so%20affordable%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Satyam%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cost%20reduction%20of%20our%20device%20to%20Rs%2012%2C000%20is%20a%20significant%20achievement%20when%20compared%20to%20similar%20products%20from%20international%20companies%20like%20YSI%2C%20Hanna%2C%20and%20WTW%2C%20which%20are%20priced%20between%20Rs%2097%2C000%20and%20Rs%202%2C63%2C000.%20The%20high%20costs%20of%20these%20competing%20products%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20factors%20such%20as%20import%20duties%2C%20limited%20after-sales%20support%2C%20and%20high%20operational%20expenses%20as%20these%20products%20are%20not%20made%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20approach%20to%20bringing%20down%20costs%20involved%20using%20industrial-grade%20water%20sensors%20and%20leveraging%20Google%E2%80%99s%20free%20web%20hosting%20and%20real-time%20database%20services.%20This%20strategic%20choice%20not%20only%20made%20our%20device%20affordable%20but%20also%20integrated%20it%20with%20cutting-edge%20IoT%20capabilities.%20We%20developed%20this%20product%20in-house%20at%20the%20Enzyme%20and%20Microbial%20Technology%20Lab%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChallenges%20in%20developing%20the%20device%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20development%2C%20Satyam%2C%20his%20mentor%20and%20colleagues%20encountered%20challenges%20related%20to%20power%20distribution%2C%20weight%20balancing%2C%20and%20maintaining%20a%20compact%20design.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20these%20issues%2C%20they%20made%20several%20adjustments%2C%20including%20redesigning%20the%20case%20and%20the%20outer%20structure%20to%20improve%20buoyancy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20integrated%20a%2020%2C000%20mAh%20high%20endurance%20battery%20to%20ensure%20longer%20operational%20times%20when%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294472%2Fair-conditioner-ac-works-on-solar-panel-energy-reduce-electricity-bill%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20not%20in%20use.%20Further%20refinements%20were%20made%20to%20enhance%20the%20smooth%20processing%20and%20display%20of%20data%2C%20ultimately%20overcoming%20the%20initial%20challenges