0put%20these%20thoughts%20in%20their%20mind.%20We%20wonder%20who%20will%20take%20care%20of%20the%20child.%20Firstly%2C%20tell%20yourself%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20and%20know%20that%20your%20child%20will%20be%20taken%20care%20of.%20He%20or%20she%20is%20in%20good%20hands%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVedansh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20few%20months%20short%20of%2020%20today%2C%20runs%20their%20family%E2%80%99s%20ice-cream%20parlour%20in%20Mumbai.%20According%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20he%20has%20great%20willpower%20and%20runs%20an%20Instagram%20account%2C%20%E2%80%98motivation.vedansh%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20inspire%20others%20through%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clear%20glimpse%20of%20his%20resilience%20was%20witnessed%20in%202016%2C%20when%20he%20had%20to%20undergo%20a%20life-threatening%20spine%20surgery.%20As%20the%20doctors%20wheeled%20him%20in%20for%20surgery%2C%20Vedansh%20insisted%20that%20his%20mother%20stay%20by%20his%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20surgery%20took%208.5%20hours%2C%20and%20the%20then%2012-year-old%2C%20was%20on%20a%20ventilator%20for%20a%20week.%20The%20moment%20he%20woke%20up%20after%20five%20days%20was%20the%20best%20in%20Moushmi%E2%80%99s%20life.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20promised%20my%20mumma%20that%20I%20would%20come%20off%20the%20ventilator%2C%20hale%20and%20hearty.%20And%20so%20I%20did%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vedansh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%2040%20days%2C%20he%20was%20back%20at%20school%20and%20amazed%20everyone%20with%20his%20will%20power.%20Seeing%20her%20child%20flourish%20and%20cope%20with%20every%20challenge%20that%20came%20his%20way%20gave%20Moushmi%20the%20motivation%20to%20do%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20child%20is%20not%20complaining%2C%20why%20should%20I%3F%20He%20is%20never%20frustrated%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20throw%20any%20tantrums.%20He%20got%20to%20terms%20with%20his%20disease%20and%20accepted%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Moushmi.